<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.4666649>
        a                        fabio:Figure ;
        dc:description           "Figure 1. Proterops nigripennis Wesmael, female, The Netherlands, Uffelte. (A) Wings. (B) Outer hind claw. (C) Scapus and pedicellus, lateral aspect. (D) Hind leg. (E) Head, dorsal aspect. (F) Mesosoma, dorsal aspect. (G) Head, anterior aspect. (H) Detail of vein 1-M of fore wing. (I) Apex of antenna. (J) Antenna. (K) Habitus, lateral aspect. (L) First to third metasomal tergites, dorsal aspect. Scale bars: 1.0X(A,D,J,K); 5.0X(B,C,I); 2.0X(E,G,H); 1.3X(F, L)." ;
        fabio:hasRepresentation  "https://zenodo.org/record/4666649/files/figure.png" .

